Description: Handle of pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp?
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.31, 48. This does not seem to be the same piece as British Museum 2011,5003.413 or 2011,5004.60, though the die may well be the same.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.1475)
